article.description: — KJ Jenkins had 21 points as New Mexico romped past Denver 87-67 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Jenkins scores 21 to carry New Mexico over Denver 87-67
article.linkText: Jenkins scores 21 to carry New Mexico over Denver 87-67
article.story: ALBUQUERQUE, N.M. -- — KJ Jenkins had 21 points as New Mexico romped past Denver 87-67 on Thursday night. Gethro Muscadin had 12 points and 11 rebounds for New Mexico (6-4). Jamal Mashburn Jr. added 10 points. Jay Allen-Tovar had 10 rebounds and three blocks. Jaelen House, whose 19 points per game heading into the matchup was second on the Lobos, was held to nine points on 4-of-10 shooting. Coban Porter had 19 points for the Pioneers (3-8), whose losing streak stretched to five games. Jordan Johnson added 12 points. KJ Hunt had 10 points and seven assists. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
